# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Day In The Life Of A Temple University Student

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A RenPy game where the user goes through a day in the life of a temple university student. They get to pick the major from 5 options: English/Psychology/Computer Science/Art History/Finance 

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

Our game will be like a chose/build your own adventure game, in which the user gets to chose if they want to skip class/want to go to certain classes and that will give an output of whether or not that was a good decision or not. 
Then at the end of the day the user can see all the other instances of what couldve been. It will be executed mainly through elif/if/else statements (hopefully). It will have choice features that effect the code and in what direction it goes. 
For example, whether you choose to talk to a friend or go to a study group would effect the outcomes of at the end of the day. At the end of the day you get a tally of how well you did based on the decisions made. 

